{
  "stem": "23350.5",
  "chunk_idx": 8,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 5.1,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 32,
      "text": "But we were sent-- had-- first of all, we had to get well.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 33,
      "text": "And whilst I was in Windermere, one day, I received a letter which had a picture of my sister.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 34,
      "text": "It was strange, because there was my sister and two men.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 35,
      "text": "And I-- I didn't know who they were.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 36,
      "text": "I couldn't read it, because it was in English.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 37,
      "text": "Well, apparently, what I found out is my sister was married-- got married.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 38,
      "text": "And the man who was looking for family was a pilot, a British pilot who came from Leeds, which is not so far from Windermere, Lake District.",
      "word_count": 27
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 39,
      "text": "And he was looking for me.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 40,
      "text": "And he found me on the list.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 41,
      "text": "He found a Munter on the list, but he didn't know that I would be the sister.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 42,
      "text": "My sister never believed it will be me.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 43,
      "text": "So she thought it's a cousin.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 44,
      "text": "And on the very first letter-- and she found out that this is her youngest sister.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 45,
      "text": "There was great joy.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 46,
      "text": "And my brother-in-law, who is-- was a wonderful man, really, he wrote me such a wonderful letter that now they found me.",
      "word_count": 22
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 47,
      "text": "And they-- they want now to find his brother.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 48,
      "text": "He wants to find his younger brother.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 49,
      "text": "And then we would be a family together.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 30,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 50,
      "text": "But of course, his brother didn't survive.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "[SIGHS] Yes.",
      "word_count": 2
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "We didn't know exactly, but we were very afraid.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "When they took so many people with small children and ill people, that wasn't a good sign.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "That was very bad.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "Young people, they needed for work.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "There were all sorts of young people, but that meant because they didn't want so many people.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 31,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Because they wanted to destroy us all.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Why are we survivors all together?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Because they still needed us.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 32,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "They needed us to do their work.",
      "word_count": 7
    }
  ],
